title: The Entrepreneur's Guide to Customer Development - Brant Cooper
description:
The epub was manually created using:
- PDF XChange Editor 3.0 to OCR to PDF the scanned document
- Atlantis Word Processor to effectively copy-paste as RichText from the OCR PDF and adjust most of the text.
All the automated converters failed miserably, so 8 hours of donkey work :(
- Sigil to cleanup and optimize the final epub
- This is an export from Calibre

Enjoy,
Nobody.


The Entrepreneur's Guide to Customer Development: A Cheat Sheet to the Four Steps to the Epiphany
Brant Cooper & Patrick Vlaskovits
